{"tid":949764,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"飲茶要再洗餐具真係好on9","createTime":"2018-12-21T04:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T05:11:48.000Z","uid":124712,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4254f23ac0cfb3184df39b3fb364b8678739bc98","tid":949764,"uid":124712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"本身茶樓都會洗，不過就係因為預你茶客又翻洗，好多都尻流流洗到仲有漬<br />\n<br />\n幾時先會進步到唔洗茶客自己洗<br />\n<br />\n唔想洗唔係因為懶，我屋企成日洗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而係成個格調好撚老套，大排檔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464281eefae55dbc0e1f7f69f5fdfffea35e76d0","tid":949764,"uid":82450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"你老母仲老套"},{"pid":"fc50cee9cd1a7c99f5f796a486981051f2611745","tid":949764,"uid":124712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"464281eefae55dbc0e1f7f69f5fdfffea35e76d0","tid":949764,"uid":82450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"你老母仲老套"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"On9仔。不報來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec6f43092202f01dce027b805d15d0a3a197b2f","tid":949764,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"唔會洗，你果兜咁既熱水首先個兜都已經唔知乾唔乾淨<br />\n洗洗下又已經唔係100度<br />\n隊埋隻污糟手落去一齊轉轉轉<br />\n轉完一輪變左兜污糟水又再放另一批野落去兜污糟水繼續轉<br />\n根本就哂氣，洗咩洗<br />\n本身就有茶漬就屌班人叫佢直接換過隻啦，一係就本身間野都污糟"},{"pid":"ba27ca974689ec29c05dc30374662cd2f42558f8","tid":949764,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"弱鳩智 咁你咪唔好洗自己個套囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8049d383ea2f4699c1adb8879694e80a19a608b7","tid":949764,"uid":124712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba27ca974689ec29c05dc30374662cd2f42558f8","tid":949764,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"r